# BerryCore Binary Catalog
# Format: binary_name|category|description
# Lines starting with # are comments

# Development Tools
autoconf|dev|Automatic configure script builder
automake|dev|Tool for generating Makefile.in files
bison|dev|Parser generator (yacc replacement)
cflow|dev|C program call graph analyzer
flex|dev|Fast lexical analyzer generator
gcc|dev|GNU Compiler Collection (C/C++)
gdb|dev|GNU Debugger (if available)
git|dev|Distributed version control system
m4|dev|Macro processor
make|dev|Build automation tool
patch|dev|Apply diff files to originals

# Shells
bash|shell|Bourne Again Shell
zsh|shell|Z Shell with advanced features

# Text Editors
ed|editor|Line-oriented text editor
nano|editor|Simple, user-friendly text editor
vim|editor|Vi IMproved text editor

# Core Utilities (from coreutils)
ls|util|List directory contents
cat|util|Concatenate and display files
cp|util|Copy files and directories
mv|util|Move/rename files
rm|util|Remove files and directories
grep|util|Search text using patterns
find|util|Search for files in directory hierarchy
sed|util|Stream editor for filtering/transforming text
awk|util|Pattern scanning and processing language
tar|util|Archive files (tape archive)
gzip|util|Compress files
gunzip|util|Decompress gzip files
bzip2|util|Compress files with bzip2
xz|util|Compress files with xz

# Networking Tools
curl|net|Transfer data from/to servers
wget|net|Download files from the web
ssh|net|Secure shell client
sshpass|net|Non-interactive SSH password provider
rsync|net|Remote file synchronization
nmap|net|Network exploration and security scanner
nc|net|Netcat - network utility
dropbear|net|Lightweight SSH server/client

# Version Control
git|vcs|Distributed version control
tig|vcs|Text-mode interface for Git

# System Tools
tmux|sys|Terminal multiplexer
htop|sys|Interactive process viewer
lsof|sys|List open files
file|sys|Determine file type
which|sys|Locate a command

# Security & Cryptography
openssl|security|SSL/TLS toolkit and cryptography library

# Archiving & Compression
tar|archive|Create/extract tar archives
gzip|archive|GNU zip compression
bzip2|archive|High-quality data compressor
xz|archive|XZ compression utility
unzip|archive|Extract ZIP archives

# Multimedia
ffmpeg|media|Audio/video converter and streamer
youtube-dl|media|Download videos from YouTube and others

# Data Processing
jq|data|Command-line JSON processor
sqlite3|data|SQLite database shell
bc|data|Arbitrary precision calculator

# X11 Applications
xeyes|x11|Classic X11 demo - eyes follow cursor

# JavaScript Engines
qjsc|js|QuickJS compiler
quickjs_simple_console|js|QuickJS simple REPL
quickjs_shell_console|js|QuickJS shell interface
quickjs_web_console|js|QuickJS web-based console
quickjs_web_console_es5|js|QuickJS web console (ES5)

# Programming Languages
pforth|lang|Portable ANS Forth interpreter (v28)

# Calendar & Time
gcal|time|GNU calendar program
calcurse|time|Text-based calendar and scheduling

# IRC & Communication
irc|comm|IRC client

# Games
nbsdgames|game|Collection of BSD games

# Documentation
man|doc|Display manual pages
groff|doc|GNU troff document formatting system

# Build Tools (additional)
autoheader|build|Create template header for configure
autoreconf|build|Update configure scripts
aclocal|build|Generate aclocal.m4
libtool|build|Generic library support script

# System Configuration
sc|calc|Spreadsheet calculator
task|todo|Command-line todo list manager

